      • search

        public void search​(java.lang.String type,
                   Range range,
                   java.util.List<Location> locs)
        search() searches Locations of a given type with in a given Range and modifies a parameter locs to include all search results. If this leafnode contains a location with given type and the coordinate of this location is in the given range, we add the location to the List of Locations locs
        Specified by:
        search in class BaseNode
        Parameters:
        type - the type of Location we want to search
        range - the search Range
        locs - a list of Locations containing the search results (mofify in-place)
